Package: folio-okapi
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${misc:Pre-Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, adduser (>= 3.113~), curl, openjdk-8-jre | openjdk-8-jdk | openjdk-11-jre | openjdk-11-jdk, postgresql-client, whiptail (>= 0.52.18~), bash (>= 4.3~)
Suggests: postgresql
Description: FOLIO message broker
 Okapi is the central message broker between all modules of FOLIO. It needs a 
 Postgres database to work, but that doesn't have to be a local one. This
 package is atm only a test and not meant to be distributed among a wider 
 audience.
